title: Fourchette a Bicyclette
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Delivery, Take-out, European, French, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Restaurant and delivery bike in the the Saint Boniface area. Proposes new menu each week using seasonal and organic products. Daily a soup, two starters (warm or cold), a vegetarian dish, and a non-veg dish, and two dessert.
